   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Year 15 of Imperator Caesar Titus Aelius Hadrianus Antoninus Augustus Pius, Mesore 7 for the account of Epeiph. Paid by Herak( ) son of Didas the son of Didas, his mother being Sarap( ), for poll-tax of the fifteenth year in the Syriake district twenty drachmas, that is, 20, with additional payments of ten bronze obols.</ab>
